:"同老豆老母好似FD咁傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cde9a49b89e2cb051a06361fc0e9f2e1c27aa23","tid":260070,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:52:46.000Z","msg":"一傾就嘈<br />\n屋企人成日講錢<br />\n成日開口埋口就話撞到我d中學同學做督察搵幾多幾多叫我去做<br />\n次次加人工就要我加家用, 仲要加家用個筆仲多過我份人工都on99<br />\n有次直情同佢講再係咁我辭職唔撚做<br />\n<br />\n屋企縱阿哥<br />\n佢結婚搬走左之後d野又唔搬走仲留左係間房度搞到我冇房用<br />\n然後係廳佢地又要睇電視唔比我打機睇動畫睇劇個d<br />\n<br />\n所以而家直情連飯都唔返屋企食<br />\n係街鳩流流到9點10點先返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f312cc906aa712a875320903f5b3d26d7a434a5f","tid":260070,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:07:01.000Z","msg":"好多年無同屋企人傾過計<br />\n早2日老豆入左院<br />\n都係收左工去望左佢2眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017d93e6ee05dab1531ed71a92919f9673b40b6e","tid":260070,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"九時啲親戚同佢啲仔女去旅行<br />\n佢就話要去<br />\n但我根本唔想同佢地去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以未去過"},{"pid":"159ee6fc3b58918f7b659e8c454eeb8139c9eca0","tid":260070,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>same 我覺得好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係 唔知做乜鳩"},{"pid":"36eecbd426590dab395babf3b8520966af2de3f6","tid":260070,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"同阿媽就唔會<br />\n同老豆就會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604f1962f97a6df438a12452a7ed237168fb16e0","tid":260070,"uid":43127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:05:51.000Z","msg":"好撚老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750a110ec0f0b65c22a1a001c215